{"tid":232317,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[未打招呼]GoBee.Bike疑非法霸佔咪錶位　區議員：濫用公共資源","createTime":"2017-05-06T16:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T00:37:54.000Z","uid":105567,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f5400eddff771a5a43a0bd696cad58dc7ea5f5e6","tid":232317,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T16:18:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/89101?utm_content=buffer9e9e4&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F89101%3Futm_content%3Dbuffer9e9e4%26utm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%2Bhk01%26utm_campaign%3Dbuffer&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=3f17324d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/89101?utm_content=buffer9e9e4&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/562883/xlarge/161b7a59ae928dac6aa7665112eeb602.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F562883%2Fxlarge%2F161b7a59ae928dac6aa7665112eeb602.jpg&h=4c0545cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有馬鞍山居民投訴Gobee.Bike停泊在汽車咪錶位，阻礙使用停車場。（李世榮提供）<br />\n<br />\n智能單車共享系統Gobee.Bike上月啟用以來，一直問題不斷，包括信用卡系統有漏洞、單車被棄置於城門河等。不過馬鞍山居民今日（5日）發現Gobee.Bike非法霸佔車位組裝單車，有區議員批評該公司濫用公共資源，擔心情況會繼續惡化，對當區居民造成不便。<br />\n<br />\n沙田區區議員李世榮表示，今日下午約3時收到馬鞍山居民的投訴，指在西沙路及恆智街交界的一個公眾停車場內，發現GoBee.Bike的職員將數十架單車停泊在公眾咪錶位，並進行組裝工程，認為該批單車應該是剛運送下來，工人正在進行組裝。<br />\n<br />\n李世榮批評該公司行為猶如濫用公共資源，「係使用公共資源做牟利嘅商業行為。」而且他擔心當共享單車的數量漸增時，會令情況失控，如更多共享單車胡亂擺放，以及佔用公共單車的停泊位等，對當區居民造成滋擾。他認為政府應設法例規管共享單車，並將在下周二的區議會會議上討論有關問題。<br />\n<br />\n警方：已作口頭警告<br />\n<br />\n警方回應《香港01》查詢指，警員於今日中午約12時40分巡邏時期間，發現GoBee.Bike的員工在上址搬運貨物，已立即聯絡該公司負責人，並要求對方盡快將貨物搬離上址，以免阻礙其他公眾人士使用該停車場。GoBee.Bike的員工於下午約5時完成清理現場，期間警方向該公司負責人發出一個口頭警告。"},{"pid":"13646ab0c970c74fa715ce93df14df3e5ba66c9a","tid":232317,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T16:22:05.000Z","msg":"嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幅圖真係好似係佢私家車場咁喎"},{"pid":"3e8e1176ccb372a223ae9c3c03fe955f80a74781","tid":232317,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T00:52:03.000Z","msg":"點可以咁 ?"},{"pid":"371a74dee2673f5a5b99145b84e6d5a8bf6d68c6","tid":232317,"uid":29874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:19:19.000Z","msg":"所以好多國家都係政府牽頭做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5565bba4932babe7f5e8691e7864bec90ca433f2","tid":232317,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:50:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以好多國家都係政府牽頭做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起多啲單車俓先啦"},{"pid":"66f541d1e9b946ce029540eee50dde9c6847298d","tid":232317,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:56:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連登仔個個唔係住嗰頭，關佢撚事仲好支持"},{"pid":"4f2f6d8c5db99442383eae4f699b8cbf31e0e79c","tid":232317,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T02:14:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幅圖真係好似係佢私家車場咁喎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同環保斗個法律罅一樣之嗎<br />\n<br />\n無聽過有咨詢，信間公司有政府支持嗰個係傻仔"},{"pid":"ffc9b8e790fe378c4859ca90b4aa099be243d2a3","tid":232317,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T02:17:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78954c08e22d8f3d6a2720190394f28ebf90b3a9","tid":232317,"uid":10064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T02:22:01.000Z","msg":"做咩唔每架單車炒張牌？"},{"pid":